title: In The Groove 3 Song Package
description:
In The Groove 3 Song Package

ITG 3 was never actually released due to a lawsuit against Roxor Games filed by Konami, but this almost-complete song package still exists. Enjoy!

(NOTE: I'm not responsible of the fact that some folders, for example Ra and Snow Stream are incomplete, nor the fact that some tracks are missing their Novice, Hard or Expert steps. They weren't there when I got the package in the first place.)
